## Design Requirements

### Blog Listing Page (`blog/page.tsx`)

**Layout:**
- Hero section with page title "Latest Nail Art Inspiration"
- Search/filter bar (categories, tags)
- Grid of blog cards: 3 columns desktop, 2 tablet, 1 mobile
- Pagination at bottom
- Use `container-standard` wrapper

**Blog Card Design (`BlogCard.tsx`):**
- Featured image (16:9 aspect ratio)
- Category tag (small, uppercase, #252220)
- Post title (H3, Jeremiah font, 22-24px)
- Excerpt (2 lines, Crimson Text)
- Author name + date (14px, light gray)
- Hover: lift effect (translateY -4px)
- Link entire card to post

**Spacing:**
- 40px gap between cards
- 80px between hero and grid
- 60px before pagination

---

### Single Blog Post (`blog/[slug]/page.tsx`)

**Layout Structure:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Reading Progress Bar (top, fixed)      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                         │
│  ┌───────────────────┬───────────────┐ │
│  │                   │               │ │
│  │   Main Content    │   Sidebar     │ │
│  │   (70%)           │   (30%)       │ │
│  │                   │               │ │
│  │   - Hero Image    │   - Author    │ │
│  │   - Title         │   - TOC       │ │
│  │   - TLDR Box      │   - Related   │ │
│  │   - Article Body  │   - Ads       │ │
│  │   - Images        │   - Newsletter│ │
│  │   - Comments      │               │ │
│  │                   │               │ │
│  └───────────────────┴───────────────┘ │
│                                         │
│  ┌───────────────────────────────────┐ │
│  │   Related Posts (3 cards)         │ │
│  └───────────────────────────────────┘ │
│                                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Mobile Layout:**
- Stack everything vertically
- Sidebar appears below content
- Full-width images
- Reading progress bar remains

**Components:**

1. **Hero Section:**
   - Full-width featured image
   - Category tag
   - H1 title (36-42px, Jeremiah)
   - Author, date, read time
   - Social share buttons

2. **TLDR Box (`TLDRSection.tsx`):**
   - Light background (#f9fafb with subtle border)
   - "TL;DR" heading
   - Bullet points (3-5 key takeaways)
   - Place after first paragraph

3. **Article Body (`BlogPost.tsx`):**
   - Narrow column for reading (max-w-[800px])
   - H2, H3 styled with Jeremiah
   - Paragraphs: Crimson Text, 16-18px, 1.7 line height
   - Images: Full width within column, lazy load
   - Pinterest overlay on hover
   - Inline newsletter form after 40% of content

4. **Sidebar (`BlogSidebar.tsx`):**
   - Sticky on desktop (scroll with page)
   - Author bio card
   - Table of contents (auto-generate from H2s)
   - Related posts (3-4 small cards)
   - Ad spaces (placeholder divs)
   - Newsletter signup

5. **Comments (`CommentSection.tsx`):**
   - Simple form: Name, email, message
   - Display existing comments (if any)
   - Minimal design, borders only

6. **Related Posts (`RelatedPosts.tsx`):**
   - 3 cards horizontal on desktop
   - 1 card per row on mobile
   - Small cards: image + title + date

