## Specific Component Guidelines

### BlogCard.tsx
```typescript
// Structure
- Image (aspect-16/9, hover:scale-105)
- Category badge (text-xs, uppercase, tracking-wide)
- Title (font-heading, text-xl, 2 line clamp)
- Excerpt (font-body, text-gray-600, 2 line clamp)
- Meta (author, date - text-sm, text-gray-500)
- Hover: lift + shadow
```

### BlogPost.tsx
```typescript
// Reading experience
- Max width 800px (comfortable reading)
- H2: 28-32px, margin-top 60px
- H3: 22-24px, margin-top 40px
- Paragraphs: margin-bottom 24px
- Images: margin 40px 0
- Blockquotes: left border 4px, padding-left 24px
- Lists: proper indentation, 1.6 line height
```

### ReadingProgress.tsx
```typescript
// Fixed top bar
- Height 3px
- Background #252220
- Width based on scroll %
- Z-index high (above content)
- Smooth transition
```

### Pagination.tsx
```typescript
// Simple number pagination
- Center aligned
- Numbers: 1 2 3 ... 10
- Current page: bold, underline
- Arrows: ← →
- 40px touch targets on mobile
```

