## Image Handling

### Featured Images
- Load immediately (above fold)
- Aspect ratio 16:9 or 3:2
- WebP format
- Responsive sizes

### Inline Images
- Lazy load (viewport detection)
- Pinterest save button overlay on hover
- Click to open modal (optional)
- Alt text from markdown
- Captions below if provided

---

## Typography in Posts

### Heading Hierarchy
```css
H1: 36-42px, font-heading, margin-bottom 24px
H2: 28-32px, font-heading, margin-top 60px, margin-bottom 20px
H3: 22-24px, font-heading, margin-top 40px, margin-bottom 16px
H4-H6: 18-20px, font-heading
```

### Body Text
```css
Paragraphs: 16-18px, font-body, line-height 1.7
Strong: font-weight 600
Links: underline, same color, hover opacity 0.7
Lists: 16-18px, margin-left 24px
```

