## Mobile Optimizations

### Blog Listing
- 1 column grid
- Larger touch targets (48px min)
- Cards full width
- Reduce image size
- Stack filter UI vertically

### Single Post
- No sidebar (move to bottom)
- Full-width images
- Increase font slightly (17-18px)
- Hide TOC (not needed on mobile)
- Sticky share buttons (optional)

